1. `CR-01 已修复。`
`publish_exam` 在服务调用后补了 `await db.commit()`，见 [src/edu_cloud/modules/exam/router.py](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/exam/router.py#L258) 和 [src/edu_cloud/modules/exam/router.py](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/exam/router.py#L259)。
