`create_assignment` 同样在 `assign_block()` 后提交，见 [src/edu_cloud/modules/grading/assignment_router.py](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/grading/assignment_router.py#L52) 和 [src/edu_cloud/modules/grading/assignment_router.py](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/grading/assignment_router.py#L57)。
